{"word":"Brass","slug":"brass","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Brass</b> Or more probably copper.<br/> Smelted<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=22&verse=20'>Eze 22:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=28&verse=2'>Job 28:2</a><br/> A mineral of Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=8&verse=9'>Deu 8:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=22&verse=8'>Jos 22:8</a><br/> A mineral of Syria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=8'>2Sa 8:8</a><br/> Tyrians traded in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27&verse=13'>Eze 27:13</a><br/> Abundance of, for the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=47'>1Ki 7:47</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=22&verse=14'>1Ch 22:14</a><br/> Articles made of:<br/> - Altar, vessels, and other articles of the tabernacle and temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=38&verse=31'>Exo 38:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=47'>1Ki 7:47</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=8&verse=27'>Ezr 8:27</a> <br/> - Cymbals<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=19'>1Ch 15:19</a> <br/> - Trumpets<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=13&verse=1'>1Co 13:1</a> <br/> - Armor<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=6'>1Sa 17:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=12&verse=10'>2Ch 12:10</a> <br/> - Bows<br/> <a href='S:Bow'>Bow</a> <br/> - Fetters<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=16&verse=21'>Jdg 16:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=25&verse=7'>2Ki 25:7</a> <br/> - Gates<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=107&verse=16'>Psa 107:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=45&verse=2'>Isa 45:2</a> <br/> - Bars<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=13'>1Ki 4:13</a> <br/> - Idols<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=5&verse=4'>Dan 5:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=9&verse=20'>Rev 9:20</a> <br/> - Mirrors<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=38&verse=8'>Exo 38:8</a> <br/> - Household vessels<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=7&verse=4'>Mar 7:4</a> <br/> - Money<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=10&verse=9'>Mat 10:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=12&verse=41'>Mar 12:41</a> <br/> Workers in:<br/> - Tubal-Cain<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=4&verse=22'>Gen 4:22</a> <br/> - Hiram<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=14'>1Ki 7:14</a> <br/> - Alexander<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=4&verse=14'>2Ti 4:14</a><br/><a href='S:Brazier'>Brazier</a>; <a href='S:Copper'>Copper</a>; <a href='S:Molding'>Molding</a> <br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=26&verse=19'>Lev 26:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=33&verse=25'>Deu 33:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=48&verse=4'>Isa 48:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=1&verse=18'>Jer 1:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=1&verse=7'>Eze 1:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=2&verse=32'>Dan 2:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=2&verse=39'>Dan 2:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=7&verse=19'>Dan 7:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=10&verse=6'>Dan 10:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=6&verse=1'>Zec 6:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=1&verse=15'>Rev 1:15</a>"}]}